cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.PL

The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques, particularly neural networks, for the approximate model-checking problem for continuous and hybrid systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with systems and control (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL) in the context of model checking, which further supports the inclusion of these sub-categories.
